com%2Fsingtosay%3Figshid%3D13osvd4fbrcx3&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=2a95c97b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/singtosay?igshid=13osvd4fbrcx3</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>黃瑋中 Herman </strong><br />\n啱啱出咗一隻派台大碟&lt;Let&rsquo;s Be Real&gt;，上面挽歌之聲既嗰隻《致所有對逝者之人》就係佢唱，喺香港呢個地方岀大蝶真係好勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYouTube: 黃瑋中 Herman Wong <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/whermanlol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fwhermanlol&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=2409d37d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/whermanlol</a><br />\nInstagram: @wwcherman <a href=\"https://instagram.com/wwcherman?igshid=10y3xd0yshsb0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwwcherman%3Figshid%3D10y3xd0yshsb0&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=28d84aa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/wwcherman?igshid=10y3xd0yshsb0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>更多</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港抗爭藝術平台 #FREETOBERHK2019</strong><br />\n定期收集、分享唔同同流水革命有關作品，佢哋之前喺位於富德樓既書店&mdash;&mdash;艺鵠 搞咗個叫做《抗爭的藝術》既作品展覽，佢地再搞既話好值得去睇<br />\n另外佢地都有活動，以一週一繪一主題既方式收集作品，有興趣嘅話都可以參與<br />\nInstagram: @freetober2019  <a href=\"https://instagram.com/freetoberhk2019?igshid=shy8rw7d7fj1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffreetoberhk2019%3Figshid%3Dshy8rw7d7fj1&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=af58a010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/freetoberhk2019?igshid=shy8rw7d7fj1</a><br />\n<br />\n題外話，上述睇過既書店 <strong>艺鵠 </strong>都好值得去行，有好多唔同同本土有關既書籍，同流水革有關既攝影集、書... etc. ，其實成幢富德樓都有好多得意野，淨係架𨋢已經好值得去睇，有機會一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Art and Culture Outreach 艺鵠</strong><br />\nInstagram: @artandcultureoutreach <a href=\"https://instagram.com/a