kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T00:06:29.000Z","msg":"揾到有篇報導，創辨人係咁講：<br />\n<blockquote>艺鵠書店的名字，是從英文ACO（全寫是 Art and Culture Outreach）音譯過來。有著天鵝形態、藝術之鳥的意思。至於為何選用這個「艺」字而非繁體「藝」字，創辦人May Fung 馮美華笑說：「沒甚麼原因，純粹想表現書店的與別不同。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://p-articles.com/heteroglossia/232.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp-articles.com%2Fheteroglossia%2F232.html&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=b2502ad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p-articles.com/heteroglossia/232.html</a> </blockquote><br />\n不過「艺」字除咗係簡體，都係日文漢字黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣都幾有美感"},{"pid":"6dd42e36746264fdbb0ae93e7e55fd063688f45e","tid":1958697,"uid":36329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T00:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdtApxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdtApxB.png&h=dcdf47e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企仲儲住佢出嘅漫畫<br />\n一開始係睇不軌劇場先<br />\n跟住再補返標童話集同錦鏽藍田返來<br />\n<br />\n依家已經好似好耐冇出書<br />\n對上一次去睇佢實體作品已經係一個海港城嘅展覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6859fe6e545c84f236807fb2573a256b477cf309","tid":1958697,"uid":9214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T00:16:47.000Z","msg":"好鐘意啲兩個畫畫ac<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>leftpoolstoner</strong></span><br />\n有幫莊正畫cd封面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/leftpoolstoner?igshid=2m1v34g46ns3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fleftpoolstoner%3Figshid%3D2m1v34g46ns3&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=674dd782\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/leftpoolstoner?igshid=2m1v34g46ns3</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVz7Z7M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVz7Z7M.png&h=752d4442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>siukinslll</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n啲style好特別 <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/siukinslll?igshid=vus9u58upkty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsiukinslll%3Figshid%3Dvus9u58upkty&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=7a9d8b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/siukinslll?igshid=vus9u58upkty</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsminmJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsminmJ.png&h=9be5d99c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63c4dc28cecf2b13616436873625a26f70e2e44c","tid":1958697,"uid":199727,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T00:33:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">// 我唔希望你地因為立場而欣賞我、幫襯我，而係真真正正去欣賞我做既作品，所以我唔需要你地懲罰我，只要我做得夠好，自然就會有人欣賞。」呢一件係一件好可悲既事，因為喺香港呢個冇生活既地方唔係畫得夠好就會有人欣賞，如果我地鼓吹黃色經濟、文創圈，但係唔係真心欣賞嗰個人既作品，對於一班藝術家黎，絕對係一種侮辱。當我地喺連儂牆見到一幅好靚嘅作品，係咪都應該要了解吓佢既作者？ //</span><br />\n<br />\n好認同呢段, 我覺得黃色經濟圈個概念夾硬用落文藝創作 絕對係令件事腐化咗同埋低俗咗"},{"pid":"9bb1725d53cce926f9ff3b592c90c7ab47cca41d","tid":1958697,"uid":130740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T00:33:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>攝影</ins></strong><br />\n無論係日常定抗爭，攝影無疑係一個最直接既記錄，記錄咗每一刻既感受，同本土每一個角落既美態。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>L̸C̸</strong><br />\nInstagram: @lc.lcn <a href=\"https://instagram.com/lc.lch?igshid=mprhexwd124j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flc.lch%3Figshid%3Dmprhexwd124j&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD22%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=acafe4b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/lc.lch?igshid=mprhexwd124j</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q23TVMj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ23TVMj.png&h=842e2a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Yu Chun W.</strong><br />\nInstagram: @ycpixels_ <a href=